<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> وَجَهْرُ إِمامٍ بِقِرَاءَةٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٧]</span> وَقَوْلُ غَيْرِ مَأْمُومٍ بَعْدَ التَّحْمِيدِ: <span style="color:#008000">(مِلْءَ السَّمَاءِ، وَمِلْءَ الأَرْضِ، وَمِلْءَ مَا شِئْتَ مِنْ شَيْءٍ بَعْدُ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٨]</span> <span style="color:#707070">[٩]</span> وَمَا زَادَ عَلَى مَرَّةٍ فِي تَسْبِيحٍ، وَسُؤَالِ المَغْفِرَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١٠]</span> وَدُعَاءٌ فِي تَشَهُّدٍ أَخِيرٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١١]</span> وَقُنُوتٌ فِي وِتْرٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَسُنَنُ الأَفْعَالِ مَعَ الهَيْئَاتِ:</span> خَمْسٌ وَأَرْبَعُونَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيُكْرَهُ لِلمُصَلِّي:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> الْتِفَاتٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَتَغْمِيضُ عَيْنَيْهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَمَسُّ الحَصَى، وَنَحْوُ ذَلِكَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> يُسَنُّ سُجُودُ السَّهْوِ لِلمُصَلِّي:</span> إِذَا أَتَى بِقَوْلٍ مَشْرُوعٍ فِي غَيْرِ مَحَلِّهِ سَهْوًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيُبَاحُ:</span> إِذَا تَرَكَ مَسْنُونًا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيَجِبُ:</span> إِذَا زَادَ رُكُوعًا، أَوْ سُجُودًا، أَوْ قِيَامًا، أَوْ قُعُودًا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>